dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Includes French and German scale bars. With compass rose, coat of arms, and ship illustrations. Does not match any states listed in Van der Krogt. From the Jansson Appendix Atlas 1636-1680, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map: 36 x 48 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
dct_creator_sm: Jansson, Jan, 1588-1664.,Vignaud, Henry, 1830-1922, former owner.,Jansson, Jan, 1588-1664. Appendix Atlas.
